result.title: Introduction to #Team4T's Training Ground.
result.content:
Greetings, friend!

I, thuytrang12a2, proudly present to you the Training Ground for #Team4T! This ground is created by Akikaze, and also please say hi to Team4T.NgocMai as well! As official members of #Team4T, we are the managers of this group.

You can join there and solve some coding problems. We will add problems and classify them regularly, so please check out often!

Have fun coding!
